2 How to handle multiple windows

    window_handles ----> [list of all open windows - id]
    driver.current_window_handle -- id of current window
    driver.switch_to.window



    PAGE A(P) ----> PAGE B ---> PAGE C ---> PAGE D

    driver.window_handles
            l1=[idA,idB,idC,idD]

            for i in l1:
                if idC==driver.current_window_handle:
                    driver.switch_to.window




